    "body": "I have found the issue. It is about `v` value of ECDSA signature that its value is incorrect when chain ID is large, which has been described by this PR: https://github.com/gakonst/ethers-rs/pull/1198.\r\n\r\nI also have proposed a solution in this PR, https://github.com/gakonst/ethers-rs/pull/1204, which is the same solution used by Ledger's JavaScript Library.",
